State ex rel. Bratenahl
v.
Bratenahl 2018-0440 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 6, 2018

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

APPEALS ACCEPTED FOR REVIEW Cause accepted on proposition of law No. II. Kennedy, J., would accept the cause on all propositions of law.

DeGenaro, J., would accept the cause on proposition of law Nos. II and III.

O'Connor, C.J., and O'Donnell and Fischer, JJ., dissent.
